        "comment": "The fresh and older wind slabs are lying on top of a weakly bonded old snowpack. Precarious weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on shady slopes. The weather conditions gave rise to increasing moistening of the snowpack in particular at low and intermediate altitudes."
